description: Pike spent all day cleaning his garage because the night before, his friend, was partying in it and wrecked the place. These dudes are 18 but still live at home so Pike was in serious trouble with his parents. After finally cleaning up the mess, his friend showed up. Showed up just in time to miss the clean up. But Pike knew something else that needed cleaned out. And besides his friend owed him big time. The mess Pike makes all over his virgin friend's face is way hotter than the mess in the garage.
title: Loving Pike
